title: What is the name and position of each member of Stray Kids? - Quora

response.answer_text: bang chan 방찬 birth name: christopher bang (so fans often times refer to him as chris!) position(s): leader, main producer, lead vocalist, lead dancer, sub rapper birthday: october 3rd, 1997 zodiac sign: libra sub-unit: producing unit 3racha, and in that sub-unit his stage name is cb97 (1/2 of the aussie line)  lee know 리노 birth name: lee minho 이민호 position(s): main dancer, sub vocalist, sub rapper birthday: october 25th, 1998 zodiac sign: scorpio sub-unit: dancing unit danceracha  changbin 창빈 birth name: seo changbin 서창빈 position(s): main rapper, sub vocalist, producer birthday: august 11th, 1999 zodiac sign: leo sub-unit: producing unit 3racha, and in the unit his stage name is spearb  hyunjin 현진 birth name: hwang hyunjin 황현진 position(s): main dancer, lead rapper, sub vocalist, visual birthday: march 20th, 2000 zodiac sign: pisces sub-unit: dancing unit danceracha  han 한 birth name: han jisung 한지성 english name: peter han position(s): main rapper, lead vocalist, producer birthday: september 14th, 2000 zodiac sign: virgo sub-unit: producing unit 3racha, and in this unit his stage name is j.one  felix 필릭스 birth name: felix lee 이 필릭스 korean name: lee yongbok 이용복 position(s): lead dancer, lead rapper, sub vocalist birthday: september 15th, 2000 zodiac sign: virgo sub-unit: dancing unit danceracha (2/2 of the aussie line)  seungmin 승민 birth name: kim seungmin 김승민 position(s): main vocalist birthday: september 20th, 2000 zodiac sign: virgo sub-unit: singing unit vocalracha  i.n. 아이엔 birth name: yang jeongin 양정인 position(s): sub vocalist, maknae birthday: february 8th, 2001 zodiac sign: aquarius sub-unit: singing unit vocalracha  i hope you don't mind me adding a little bit of extra info, heh… but i encourage you to stan!! their comeback is september 14th, and we think it will be their most successful one yet!
